Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like another scorcher today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.14,0:00:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's summer,\Nyet you're all bundled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.14,0:00:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?\NThat paper's three days old.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They say this time a middle-aged couple\Nin Verden was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.52,0:00:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear the killer is a doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah... You said you're going\Nto Verden, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.52,0:00:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You know someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.86,0:00:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I don't know if I can\Nmeet up with him or not, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.26,0:00:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You got your start\Nin the French Foreign Legion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,After going off on your own, you joined\Nthe fighting in Nicaragua in 1979.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,From 1981 to 1984 you aided\Nthe Afghan rebel guerillas...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.78,0:03:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In 1987, you played a central role\Nin the Mossad's secret operation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.02,0:03:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to assassinate Islamic extremists.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What a brilliant fighting record,\NHugo Bernhardt...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Since a mercenary such as you\Nis sponsoring this seminar,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you must have some\Noutstanding students graduating...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be a good idea to send\Nour young ones to attend your lectures
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and have you whip them into shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,incidentally...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:04:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this man outstanding?\NI believe he showed up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,at your training grounds\Nabout five months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He is brilliant with a scalpel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but did he show an aptitude\Nwith a pistol?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no wish to speak\Nabout my students...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever learned\Nto shoot a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:04:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're self-taught...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never shot a gun before...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Not once?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I know I'm asking\Nfor the impossible, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice\Nbut to ask you for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, anyone\Nwho comes here is asked
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to forget all he's learned about guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never had anyone\Nwho'd never shot a gun before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump rope...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of your experience,\Nthis is where everyone starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like that child...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Get busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.37,0:06:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your balance! Your balance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.18,0:07:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't do it as well as you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you always keep an eye\Non the trainees for the trainer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, you needn't glare at me\Nthat way. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I must do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a brambling...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's looking for food\Nfor its chicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you so exhausted that\Nyou've lost your appetite?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Eating is part of your training.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she your child...or, your grandchild?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That child's mother\Nwas shot and killed by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right before her eyes...in Myanmar...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,When I ran into a hut in the jungles\Nfor shelter, they were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The mother was holding a gun
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'd been a fraction\Nof a second slower,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have been shot dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why\NI brought that child here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Since she began living with me,\Nthat child has never smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll probably die hating me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When you have a gun,\Nthat sort of thing happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't like it, you're better off\Nnever picking up a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:13:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Something smells nice...\NIt smells like daphne blossoms...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Then...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for some running.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're done running,\Ncome to the low ground in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Low ground...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:13:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The firing range.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Firing range...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, twice...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever you shoot your gun,\Npull the trigger twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,By pulling the trigger twice,\Nyou raise the probability
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,that you'll get your target.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.01,0:14:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't do that,\Nconsider yourself dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.37,0:15:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always preparing meals for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so today I decided to make you\Nsome Japanese food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is called "nikujaga."\NI hope you'll like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are chopsticks.\NThey're carved out of wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought they would enhance\Nthe Japanese feel of the dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're good...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You use those chopsticks well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.27,0:16:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.47,0:17:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a brambling chick.\NI guess it fell out of its nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to return it to its nest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That chick is going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.51,0:17:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very difficult to raise it\Naway from its nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rare that you\Ncan do it successfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's return it to its nest...\Nto its mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Three seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.16,0:18:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is determined\Nin three seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's even an instant of hesitation,\Nthe one killed will be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How was his performance record\Nwhen he finished the course?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:19:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Technically, he had a perfect score,\Nand his physical condition also improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,His concentration\Nwas phenomenal. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.86,0:19:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,However?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Being able to shoot a person\Nis another issue altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.47,0:19:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether he's able to shoot\Nhis first person will determine
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.77,0:19:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,whether he will or won't be able to\Nuse his gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... I wonder which way he'll go...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, never mind about that.\NDo you have any idea where he went?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.56,0:19:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to tell me if you do know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you for everything,\Nthese five months...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:19:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Enclosed is the rest of my tuition.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And please help yourself\Nto the nikujaga.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.79,0:20:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have my sincere thanks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.82,0:20:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She laughed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it? You do know where\Nhe went, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.21,0:21:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine... You may leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
